File [NETSTAT.EXE][1] should be on the [PATH][2] (environment variable), hence your &quot;command&quot; of just _netstat_ should be enough. If `NETSTAT.EXE` is not on the PATH, you can either edit the PATH or provide the full path to the file in your Java code. On my Windows 10 machine, the path to the file is...
